  "title": "Printing Assistant - Contract Role",
  "description": "<ul><li>Work Location - East Region</li><li>Working Hours - Mon to Thurs 8am to 5pm, Fri 8am - 4.30pm</li><li>Monthly Salary - up to $2600 per month</li><li>11 Months Contract, Primary School</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Operate photocopying, binding, laminating, collating, and paper-cutting machines.</li><li>Print, distribute, and organize teaching materials, exam papers, and documents.</li><li>Track printing requests and prioritize tasks.</li><li>Maintain inventory of paper, toner, and other supplies.</li><li>Ensure Printing Room and equipment are clean and well-maintained.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum secondary school education (GCE 'N' or 'O' Level Certificate or equivalent).</li><li>Preferably 1-3 years of relevant experience in printing duties.</li><li>School environment experience preferred.</li><li>Familiarity with handling printing and laminating machine.</li><li>Able to independently operate various office machines.<br /></li></ul><p>Interested candidates, kindly email your resume to: <strong>zuli.ng@tg-hr.com</strong></p><p><strong>We regret to inform that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
